{"tid":2374702,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"特朗普 歷史之中最糟","createTime":"2021-01-21T12:10:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-21T15:06:42.000Z","uid":72497,"like":4,"dislike":13,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1742b88d27fc008ad3b1971f2d62d715e9215d9e","tid":2374702,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:10:30.000Z","msg":"(男)特朗普 歷史之中最糟<br />\n拜登 沒有一處比侵糟<br />\n(女)論政績 自有登比此侵更好<br />\n就愛心 找不到比佢好<br />\n(女)登登完美 (男)無一可比美<br />\n(女)侵侵糟<br />\n(男)登愛有如天高 (女)愛更高<br />\n更多更詳盡歌詞 在 ※ <a href=\"http://Mojim.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FMojim.com&d=PT6dGXJ5JuBAxmbDRmxpcFm6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=7c3617af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Mojim.com</a> 魔鏡歌詞網<br />\n(男)千百樣好<br />\n(合)論拜登 特朗普邊忽比佢好<br />\n或者 絕招同途異路<br />\n但我知 joe拜登joe得到更好<br />\n待你真 拜登始終美好<br />\n在我心 拜登始終美好"},{"pid":"1d21f51251dd2f22bc1068b8c94b2d28bcdddae2","tid":2374702,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"dem<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52a64f78d720a243e7f64c868eb333421fd5b7a0","tid":2374702,"uid":72497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d21f51251dd2f22bc1068b8c94b2d28bcdddae2","tid":2374702,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:10:55.000Z","msg":"dem<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:13:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"35c30e467ff511a49dc91684d3f0ee61ba75dac0","tid":2374702,"uid":121431,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:14:22.000Z","msg":"Which church are you from?"},{"pid":"12653e3b2397338f5c09b9d8c77f13b902a7e00c","tid":2374702,"uid":245484,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-21T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://encrypted-tbn0.gstatic.com/images?q=tbn:ANd9GcTxvagcailV4dGdLypHUdq6mYKAlc6